Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's popularity soars
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407c5f
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 3 Apr 1977
President Carter gets a 70 per cent popularity rating in the polls. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.